​
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Spring Boot の API を TypeScript から呼ぶ基本パターン</h4>
      <div class="code"><span class="cm">// 型定義（APIのレスポンスと合わせる）</span>
<span class="kw">interface</span> <span class="tp">UserResponse</span> {
  userId: <span class="tp">number</span>;
  name: <span class="tp">string</span>;
  email: <span class="tp">string</span>;
  createdAt: <span class="tp">string</span>;  <span class="cm">// Java の LocalDateTime は文字列で来る</span>
}
​
<span class="kw">interface</span> <span class="tp">UserCreateRequest</span> {
  name: <span class="tp">string</span>;
  email: <span class="tp">string</span>;
  age: <span class="tp">number</span>;
}
​
<span class="kw">interface</span> <span class="tp">ErrorResponse</span> {
  errorCode: <span class="tp">string</span>;
  message: <span class="tp">string</span>;
  errors: <span class="tp">string</span>[] | <span class="kw">null</span>;
}
​
<span class="cm">// API呼び出し関数（async/await）</span>
<span class="kw">const</span> <span class="mt">createUser</span> = <span class="kw">async</span> (data: <span class="tp">UserCreateRequest</span>): <span class="tp">Promise</span>&lt;<span class="tp">UserResponse</span>&gt; =&gt; {
  <span class="kw">const</span> response = <span class="kw">await</span> <span class="mt">fetch</span>(<span class="st">'/api/users'</span>, {
    method: <span class="st">'POST'</span>,
    headers: { <span class="st">'Content-Type'</span>: <span class="st">'application/json'</span> },
    body: <span class="tp">JSON</span>.<span class="mt">stringify</span>(data),
  });
​
  <span class="kw">if</span> (!response.ok) {
    <span class="kw">const</span> error: <span class="tp">ErrorResponse</span> = <span class="kw">await</span> response.<span class="mt">json</span>();
    <span class="kw">throw new</span> <span class="tp">Error</span>(error.message);   <span class="cm">// エラーは上位でキャッチ</span>
  }
​
  <span class="kw">return</span> response.<span class="mt">json</span>() <span class="kw">as</span> <span class="tp">Promise</span>&lt;<span class="tp">UserResponse</span>&gt;;
};
​
<span class="cm">// 使い方</span>
<span class="kw">try</span> {
  <span class="kw">const</span> user = <span class="kw">await</span> <span class="mt">createUser</span>({ name: <span class="st">'田中太郎'</span>, email: <span class="st">'tanaka@example.com'</span>, age: <span class="vl">30</span> });
  console.<span class="mt">log</span>(<span class="st">'登録成功'</span>, user.userId);
} <span class="kw">catch</span> (e) {
  console.<span class="mt">error</span>(<span class="st">'エラー'</span>, e);
}</div>
​
      <div class="alert ai-info"><span class="ai">💡</span><span>JavaのLong型はJSONでは数値で来るがJavaScriptのnumberは精度が落ちることがある（2^53以上の値）。IDが大きい場合は文字列で返す設計になっていることも。設計書を確認。</span></div>
